# Optional: a server-side Gemini API key, used as a fallback when no key has been
# entered in the app's Settings panel. Useful if you're self-hosting this app just
# for yourself and don't want to paste a key into the browser every time.
#
# Get a key from https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey, copy this file to
# .env.local, and fill in the value below. .env.local is git-ignored.
GEMINI_API_KEY=
